body: https://secure.actblue.com/donate/lateefah-for-congress-uplift?refcode=X_110124_thankyou [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/lateefah-for-congress-uplift?refcode=X_110124_thankyou] Hey Friend, With just FOUR[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/lateefah-for-congress-uplift?refcode=X_110124_thankyou] days left until Election Day, my heart isfull of gratitude. Thursday marked our final end-of-month deadline for thecycle, and once again, you all showed up beyond my highest hopes. Thanks toyou, we hit our fundraising goal, and, for that, I can’t thank you enough. Ourcampaign has been a true community effort from day one, and that community isstronger than ever. But Friend, as we head into these final days, we need tokeep pushing with everything we’ve got. Right now, our greatest strength isour organizing — talking to friends, family, neighbors, everyone — to makesure CA-12 knows what’s at stake. This isn’t just about one election. It’sabout safeguarding our democracy, standing up for CA-12, and championing thevalues that unite us. So, if you’re able, please consider chipping in one moretime to help us cross the finish line strong.[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/lateefah-for-congress-uplift?refcode=X_110124_thankyou] DONATE TODAY[https://secure.actblue.com/donate/lateefah-for-congress-uplift?refcode=X_103124_eom_c] Make sure you have a plan to vote here[https://www.sos.ca.gov/elections/] , if you haven’t already. Let’s win this,folks. With all my gratitude, Lateefahhttps://secure.actblue.com/donate/lateefah-for-congress-uplift?refcode=X_110124_thankyou [https://secure.actblue.com/donate/lateefah-for-congress-uplift?refcode=X_110124_thankyou] Lateefah Simon has spent hercareer fighting for justice—fighting for folks without a voice. Now, as a25-year veteran organizer and nationally recognized advocate for civil rightsand social justice, she’s running to take this fight to Congress. In Lateefah,CA-12 has a fighter.
